# Feature catalog maintenance

[docs/feature-catalog.md](../../docs/feature-catalog.md) is the **canonical UI feature index**.

## When to update

| Trigger | Action |
|---------|--------|
| New Angular route | Add row with route, roles, happy-path steps |
| Route removed or renamed | Update or remove row |
| New menu entry or navigation path | Update step counts |
| New dev persona in `dev-import.sql` | Update Dev personas table |

## Do not duplicate

Link to [ARCHITECTURE.md](../../ARCHITECTURE.md) for technical API detail. Feature catalog is for **click paths** and **roles**, not endpoint signatures.

